{"tid":871113,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【二手劈價】一城3房不足一個月平230萬 重返今年首季價","createTime":"2018-10-21T15:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T09:43:10.000Z","uid":174649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ad177fef43e35cdc6a8c5c6f9ba694a95a21d83d","tid":871113,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T15:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181021/large/1540124365_aa7c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181021%2Flarge%2F1540124365_aa7c.png&h=0bfe0ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中原地產黎宗文表示，沙田第一城14座低層D室，實用853方呎，3房套間隔及工人套房，望內園景，以1,030萬元易手，呎價12,075元。原業主1995年11月以310萬元買入，持貨23年，賬面獲利720萬元，單位升值2.3倍。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，上月尾同類單位成交約1,260萬元，為15座中層D室，實用853方呎，呎價14,771元。目前新成交單位相差18%，除了因為單位內櫳分別之外，是次成交單位低層無景觀，兼鄰近附近發電站。至於同類低層3房戶，今年4至5月成交價介乎883萬元至910萬元。"},{"pid":"afebf3ac8fae5860d0c1e45c64402cb2addf3698","tid":871113,"uid":68550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T16:17:53.000Z","msg":"有工人房唔計"},{"pid":"31e27992a3e1f164ea1d5f4e9d516930f7425cbb","tid":871113,"uid":112720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"低層無景觀，兼鄰近附近發電站<br />\n<br />\n唔計"},{"pid":"1d25b05435449351499bd0acb9a87b21bfeb2163","tid":871113,"uid":33125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T23:58:50.000Z","msg":"據了解，上月尾同類單位成交約1,260萬元，為15座中層D室，實用853方呎，呎價14,771元。目前新成交單位相差18%，除了因為單位內櫳分別之外，是次成交單位低層無景觀，兼鄰近附近發電站。至於同類低層3房戶，今年4至5月成交價介乎883萬元至910萬元。<br />\n<br />\n淡淡繼續 j標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20a00cb2e31cfc8ab397fa0dcf1f80f5e9fbd0d","tid":871113,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:29:38.000Z","msg":"咁平 一定未補地價 唔計"},{"pid":"87c5b3fe4c6a39a